Author: umargill
Title: [ANN][RAYS] Rays Network | C-DPoS | Bulletproof | Flexible Blockchain Network |
Body: It is an extension of DPoS. In DPoS, the delegates are chosen by the community. According to the video description, in CDPOS, delegates are assigned the labels of 'Efficient', based on their performance. Efficient delegates will get more chance of block creation than other delegates.

Author: umargill
Title: [ANN][RAYS] Rays Network | C-DPoS | Bulletproof | Flexible Blockchain Network |
Body: The quantum computer attacks are the ability of extremely fast computers to overcome the difficulty level of the hash function. The ASIC miners spend a lot of energy to solve a cryptographic problem. At the same time, they spend a lot of energy to solve the cryptographic puzzle. Quantum computers, on the other hand, will be able to solve these puzzles in no time. The bulletproof algorithm is immune to such attacks from quantum proof and the privacy shield cannot be broken by the quantum computers.
